 #+liber-documentation
 "@version{#2024-05-09}
  @argument[model]{a @class{gtk:tree-model-sort} object}
  @begin{short}
    This resets the default sort function to be in the 'unsorted' state.
  @end{short}
  That is, it is in the same order as the child model. It will re-sort the
